@Article{	  Dutta:2006aa,
  abstract	= {Operational risk is being recognized as an important risk
		  component for financial institutions as evinced by the
		  large sums of capital that are allocated to mitigate this
		  risk. Therefore, risk measurement is of paramount concern
		  for the purposes of capital allocation, hedging, and new
		  product development for risk mitigation. We perform a
